desc: Introducing Shady Cat Social Club's line of Feline Euphorics- a wide selection of premium organic catnip & silver vine. We discard most of the catnip plant, only packing the *magic* that kitties LOVE- leaves & flowers! Our thoughtfully crafted products in ecofriendly packaging are truly superior & your cat deserves it!

layout.text: Shady Cat Social Club offers premium organic catnip & silver vine in a wide variety of options. We have great gifts for the shady cat or cat lover in your life!
